name: Mentorship Craft Social
desc: Kick off the Spring semester with the ACM-W Mentorship Program! Join us for our first meeting featuring fun activities like Legos, watercolor bookmarks, and coloring books, all while bonding with your Big or Little. Everyone is welcome to attend and apply to join the program! Refreshments, craft supplies, and good company provided!

name: OSU STEM Day
desc: STEM Day is an interactive outreach event hosted at OSUâ€™s Fontana Laboratories that introduces middle and high school students to engineering through facility tours and hands-on activities led by student organizations. Attendees rotate through small-group sessions, engage with volunteers, and explore different STEM disciplines in a fun, supportive environment.

name: Northside Branch Volunteering
desc: Start off the new year with ACM-W at our Vision Board Making Event! Bring your aspirations to life by crafting a personalized vision board filled with images and words that reflect your ambitions for 2026. Materials will be provided.

name: Job Fair Prep Jamboree
desc: Join us for an interactive career fair preparation event. We will have stations for you to get your resume reviewed, enhance your LinkedIn profile, practice your elevator pitch, and more. Whether you're looking for an internship or a full time role, just starting your job search, or looking to refine your skills, this event is for you!

name: Spring Kickoff 2026
desc: Discover a welcoming community for women and nonbinary individuals in technology! If you're seeking professional development or connections in tech, this is the perfect opportunity. Join ACM-W for our first Spring event featuring a preview of exciting upcoming events this semester, accompanied by delicious Adriatico's pizza. Stick around afterward for fun activities to connect and bond with fellow members. We can't wait to see you there!
